title: Black & Decker The Complete Guide to Patios by Phil Schmidt
description:
Black & Decker The Complete Guide to Patios: Plan, Build and Maintain by Phil Schmidt


Outdoor living made elegant
Patios have been featured in landscapes for thousands of years, but never have they been more popular than now, as homeowners discover the elegance, long life, and easy maintenance of stone and decorative concrete surfaces. 

Today's homeowners can build with mosaic tiles just like the ancient Persians, or natural stone like the Greeks, but they also build amazing patios with colored, interlocking concrete pavers cast in geometric shapes, or they can stamp or stain poured concrete for truly amazing effects.

Genre: Non-Fiction, Educational
